DTSTAMP:20260408T030258Z
DTSTART:20260415T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description    A webinar interview with GSBA's Director of Poli
	cy and Advocacy\, Gabriel Neuman\, and GSBA's lobby team\, Katie Kolan\, J
	ean Leonard\, and Annie McGrath. Have questions about the millionaire tax\
	, automated license plate readers\, the name change process\, or state bud
	get? We've got you covered. We will discuss hot topics that came up during
	 this legislative sessions\, GSBA's work in Olympia\, and recent legislati
	ve changes that will impact the small business community. April 15\, 12-1p
	m. Interview conversation with time for Q\\+A. Want to start the conversat
	ion now? Read over our most recent blog post on the 2026 WA Legislative Se
	ssion Recap.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/2026-legisla
